# Title: RunDLL32 Spawning Explorer
# Author: elhoim, CD_ROM_
# Date: 2022-04-27
# Level: high
# Description: Detects RunDLL32.exe spawning explorer.exe as child, which is very uncommon, often observes Gamarue spawning the explorer.exe process in an unusual way
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218.011
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_rundll32_spawn_explorer.yml

Image="*\\explorer.exe" ParentImage="*\\rundll32.exe" NOT ParentCommandLine="*\\shell32.dll,Control_RunDLL*"